NOTE ON THE SOURCE MATERIAL AND DATASET

The MIT license above covers the code in this repository. It does NOT purport
to license the underlying historical documents.

The obituary texts and biographical facts are transcribed from the U.S.
Military Academy Association of Graduates annual reports, 1870-1941, digitized
by the USMA Library and served from the USMA Digital Library (CONTENTdm
collection `aogreunion`). These source publications are early-20th-century and
earlier institutional documents; consult the USMA Library for the authoritative
statement of their rights status before any commercial reuse of the transcribed
text. Every record in this dataset links back to its source page so the
original can always be verified.
